            <title>[LU-14944] MGS - MDT failed to start</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14944</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our HPC is running Lustre ver. 1.10.3 and IML ver. 4.0.3, with One MDT, two MDSs (fail-over) , six OSSs, and 36 OSTs.&#160; After rebooting, the MDT and MGS failed to start.&#160; From the IML GUI, each time to start the MDT / MGS, the process get cancelled right away.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;The 36 OSTs were offline.&#160; But i was able to manually start them up using the command:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; crm_resource&#160;-r&#160;OSTxxxxxx -p target-role -m -v Started&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My question is if i can not start the MGS - MDT from IML GUI,&#160; how can i start the MDT from the command line?&#160; Sorry for a newbie question as&#160; a new to Lustre.&#160; Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

